CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper September 22, 1945, pg. 15, reads: "Military Police - 'The situation is well in hand,' report Sgt. George D. Poindexter (left) and Sgt. William Mitchell (right) to Capt. John D. Thomas, commanding officer of Military Police Barracks here. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Military Police Sgt. George D. Poindexter, Capt. John D. Thomas, and Sgt. William Mitchell standing outside barracks
